sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Detector Services<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference Server

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>{"messages": [...], "stream": false}
    Note over Gateway: Lookup route config<br/>Inject detector config into payload

    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional mTLS (client cert)<br/>Forwarded Authorization header<br/>{"messages": [...], "detectors": {...}}

    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Invoke configured detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-language for PII)
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results

    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Forward generation request
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Chat completion response

    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Chat completion + detections
    Note over Gateway: If detections found AND<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace response content

    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback message)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>{"messages": [...], "stream": true}
    Note over Gateway: Lookup route config<br/>Inject detector config into payload

    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional mTLS (client cert)<br/>Forwarded Authorization header<br/>{"messages": [...], "stream": true, "detectors": {...}}

    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Invoke configured detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results

    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Forward generation request (streaming)

    loop SSE Chunk Stream
        vLLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE chunk
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: {...}
        Note over Gateway: Parse SSE chunk as JSON<br/>Check for detections<br/>Apply fallback on first detection
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: {...}<br/>(original or fallback chunk)
    end

    Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: [DONE]
